<div class="features"><a name="features" class="anchor"></a>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="heading">
            <h3>Less work. More workouts.</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li class="left">
                <span>Hundreds of Options</span>
                <h5>One app, hundreds of options</h5>
                <p>FitCoins are redeemable towards thousands of fitness options; including yoga, pilates, barre, gyms, boxing, and more.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="right">
                <span class="no-expiration">No Expiration</span>
                <h5>No expiration, no fees</h5>
                <p>Unlike traditional memberships and class packs, FitCoins never expire, so you can use them when you need them and save them when you don't.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="left">
                <span class="loyalty">Loyalty Rewards</span>
                <h5>Awesome loyalty rewards</h5>
                <p>TapFit rewards you for getting fit by giving you extra FitCoins when you check in at the gym or invite your friends.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="right">
                <span class="save-money">Save Money with FitCoins</span>
                <h5>Save money with FitCoins</h5>
                <p>The more you buy, the more you save! <strong>Save up to 30%</strong> on your fitness when you buy FitCoin bundles.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="left">
                <span class="exclusive-access">Ultimate Flexibility</span>
                <h5>Convenience is king</h5>
                <p>Browse through 100's of nearby studios and book workouts with a single click. Perfect for people on-the-go or who just want to try something new.</p> 
            </li>
            <li class="right">
                <span class="analytics">Track Your Fitness</span>
                <h5>Track your fitness</h5>
                <p>Automatically track your fitness, know how many times you went to the gym each week, and easily manage your fitness expenses.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div> <!-- eo .container -->
</div> <!-- eo .features -->

